  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Everything is ready for the election of the President",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The decisive vote to choose the new president will be held in Parliament this morning.",
        "Parliamentary Secretary General Dhammika Dasanayake said that all arrangements have been made for the polling. Three candidates are competing for the presidency.",
        "Acting President Ranil Wickremesinghe, Dallas Alahapperuma and National People's Power Party leader Anura Kumara Dissanayake are the three candidates. Due to this poll, measures have been taken to double the security of the Parliament and its surrounding areas.",
        "The police said that special security will be provided to the MPs coming for the polling."
      ],
